We have a new challenge for students this Fall 2022.

Take Climate Action

Take Climate Action

3DEXPERIENCE Works For Good

Achieving zero carbon emissions with the 3DEXPERIENCE platform. Use the new cloud apps developed by SOLIDWORKS engineers.

Dassault Systèmes invites you to become part of the solution to tackle climate change using the 3DEXPERIENCE platform.

Get involved in this challenge, whatever your level of technical expertise and win one of several prizes!
